            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion wedges<strong> </strong>are cooked, add them to the pot of drained quinoa with the <strong>grated carrot </strong>and <strong>chopped mint</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>roasted onion & quinoa salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680277607620-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680277607620-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680277607620-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680277607620-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1680277607620-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> salad </strong>to a bowl and squeeze over the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> – these are your <strong>lemon-dressed leaves</strong></p><p>Once cooked, slice the<strong> chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1680277611355-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1680277611355-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1680277611355-x700.jpg",
