          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1680277611355-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dollop the <strong>harissa hummus</strong> onto plates and spread it out with the back of a spoon</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced chicken </strong>over the hummus with the <strong>lemon-dressed leaves</strong> and <strong>roasted onion & quinoa salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>pumpkin seeds </strong>and<strong> black sesame seeds</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
